snippet.title: Online Social Hangout - ROBLOX
snippet.description: ROBLOX is a free online game where you make the game. Play one of our four million user-made levels and hang out with people who may be even more crazy than you. ROBLOX is not Sparta. May cause lack of sleep. All rights reserved.
